---
title: Seared Salmon & Sage Butter with Mashed Potato & Garlicky Green Beans
description: Classic ingredients don’t need much to elevate them to a sensational meal. Take this delicious salmon – it just gets simply seared then topped with a sage-infused browned butter for a meal that’s low on effort and high on taste.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ca42c0ee3f3394b544bb176-3a971468.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/seared-salmon-sage-butter-5ca42c0ee3f3394b544bb176-c0aefd01.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
